OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Feasing this evening to leave clear
OL,7,Fspells into the night. Cloud building
OL,8,Fin the west but turning chilly further
OL,9,Feast with a touch of frost possible
OL,10,Funder the light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA chilly start in places
OL,13,Fwith bright or sunny spells through
OL,14,Fthe day. The risk of a few showers
OL,15,Faround, these mainly in the afternoon.
OL,16,FFeeling slightly warmer than Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
