OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FShowers
OL,6,Flikely on Friday, these heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes. Feeling warm and humid on
OL,8,FSaturday with the chance of rain
OL,9,Fbefore turning drier but less warm on
OL,10,FSunday.
